{"storyMeta":{"storyReviewType":"NONE","storyId":"act8mini_level_act8mini_st05","storyGroup":"act8mini","storySort":5,"storyDependence":null,"storyCanShow":1,"storyCode":"","storyName":"我无惧前路何往","storyPic":"storyMainPic_level_act8mini_st05","storyInfo":"凯尔希回想起了与博士相关的往事。眼前这个熟悉而又陌生的人，真的值得她信任吗？是时候在情感上做出抉择了。","storyCanEnter":0,"storyTxt":"activities/act8mini/level_act8mini_st05","avgTag":"幕间","unLockType":"USE_ITEM","costItemType":"MATERIAL","costItemId":"STORY_REVIEW_COIN","costItemCount":1,"stageCount":0,"requiredStages":[],"prev":3,"next":5,"characters":["？？？","凯尔希","博士","Scout","可露希尔","医疗干员","普通感染者A","普通感染者B","后勤干员","特蕾西娅","娇小的卡特斯","阿米娅"]},"lines":[{"type":"header","key":"title_test","skippable":"true","mode":"BLACK_MASK","id":0},{"type":"stopmusic","id":1},{"type":"dialog","id":2},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":3},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/8/8a/Avg_bg_bg_black.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":4},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"我的说辞并不重要。于每刻践行自己的意志，才算是真正地活着。","id":5},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"去亲历这片大地吧。独属于你的思想，需要岁月来浇铸。","id":6},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"凯尔希，我希望你......","id":7},{"type":"dialog","id":8},{"type":"delay","time":"3","id":9},{"type":"text","text":"5:39 P.M. 天气/晴","id":10},{"type":"text","text":"室外，罗德岛甲板","id":11},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$drift_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/act9d0d0/m_avg_drift_loop.mp3","volume":"0.4","id":12,"musicid":0},{"type":"dialog","id":13},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":14},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":15},{"type":"image","y":"-180","fadetime":"0","xScale":"1.5","yScale":"1.5","id":16},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"3","block":"false","id":17},{"type":"imagetween","xScale":"1.5","yScale":"1.5","yFrom":"-180","yTo":"-150","duration":"20","ease":"OutQuad","block":"false","id":18},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":19},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"最近很忙吧，有许多需要处理的事。","id":20},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"适当休息也是必要的，你的生理指标近期有一些小的波动，我会持续关注。","id":21},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"对了，煌会在今晚来向你作简报，她主导了昨天的突袭作战。","id":22},{"type":"dialog","id":23},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":24},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":25},{"type":"image","id":26},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/5/53/Avg_bg_bg_rhodescom.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":27},{"type":"cameraeffect","effect":"Grayscale","keep":"true","amount":"0.7","fadetime":"0","id":28},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":29},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":30},{"type":"text","text":"1:23 A.M. 天气/雨","id":31},{"type":"text","text":"巴别塔临时作战指挥室","id":32},{"type":"dialog","id":33},{"type":"delay","time":"0.51","id":34},{"type":"playsound","key":"$doorknockquite","volume":"1","id":35},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":36},{"type":"character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","id":37},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"门外是Scout，他负责了昨夜的行动。","id":38,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/d3/Avg_char_003_kalts_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"这是他效力于巴别塔后少有的任务失败记录。","id":39,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/d3/Avg_char_003_kalts_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_048","id":40},{"type":"dialogue","name":"博士","text":"请进。","id":41,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/09/Avg_avg_npc_048.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":42},{"type":"character","id":43},{"type":"playsound","key":"$dooropenquite","id":44},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","id":45},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_026","fadetime":"1.5","id":46},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":47},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Scout","text":"指挥官，女士，你们都在。我简短说明一下昨晚的事。","id":48,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/06/Avg_avg_npc_026.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Scout","text":"小队清扫战场时，发现了可追踪的敌军痕迹。我判断这是摸清敌军位置的机会，执意循迹追击而中了埋伏。","id":49,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/06/Avg_avg_npc_026.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Scout","text":"责任在我，我愿接受军事处分。","id":50,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/06/Avg_avg_npc_026.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_048","id":51},{"type":"dialogue","name":"博士","text":"这不是一个老萨卡兹雇佣兵会做出的决断。","id":52,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/09/Avg_avg_npc_048.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_026","id":53},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Scout","text":"很可惜，那一刻我的经验并没有对我做出警示。","id":54,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/06/Avg_avg_npc_026.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_048","id":55},{"type":"dialogue","name":"博士","text":"经验不会被没发生的事唤醒。危机发生后，没有队员战死，说明撤退时你的指挥冷静、得当。","id":56,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/09/Avg_avg_npc_048.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"博士","text":"你应当得到表彰，而非处分。","id":57,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/09/Avg_avg_npc_048.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_026","id":58},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Scout","text":"我不明白这个结论是如何得出的。","id":59,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/06/Avg_avg_npc_026.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_048","id":60},{"type":"dialogue","name":"博士","text":"军队的纪律若不能做到赏罚分明，则失去存在的意义。Scout，这个道理你一定明白。","id":61,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/09/Avg_avg_npc_048.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"博士","text":"为什么那样在乎她的名誉？我需要一个理由。","id":62,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/09/Avg_avg_npc_048.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_026","id":63},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Scout","text":"......凯尔希女士，瑞卡的情况怎么样了。","id":64,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/06/Avg_avg_npc_026.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","id":65},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"她已经脱离了危险。","id":66,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/d3/Avg_char_003_kalts_1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":67},{"type":"character","id":68},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":69},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_026","id":70},{"type":"text","text":"Scout想开口说些什么，却欲言又止。","id":71},{"type":"dialog","id":72},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_048","id":73},{"type":"dialogue","name":"博士","text":"你的内心在斗争着。即使在战场上，也未见你如此为难过。若能说出你的考虑，或许我们可以......","id":74,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/09/Avg_avg_npc_048.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_026","id":75},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Scout","text":"我坚持不让瑞卡受到任何处分。","id":76,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/06/Avg_avg_npc_026.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_048","id":77},{"type":"dialogue","name":"博士","text":"因为她是个孤儿？军队的纪律可承载不了泛滥的同情心。","id":78,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/09/Avg_avg_npc_048.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_026","id":79},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Scout","text":"瑞卡的父亲曾是萨卡兹雇佣兵，死于内战。","id":80,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/06/Avg_avg_npc_026.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_048","id":81},{"type":"dialogue","name":"博士","text":"这在卡兹戴尔不算什么新鲜事。","id":82,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/09/Avg_avg_npc_048.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_026","id":83},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Scout","text":"瑞卡的母亲身患严重的矿石病，没有抚养她的能力。特蕾西娅殿下知晓此事后，一直为她们家提供经济上的资助。","id":84,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/06/Avg_avg_npc_026.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_048","id":85},{"type":"dialogue","name":"博士","text":"这也没什么特别的。如果没有更充分的理由......","id":86,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/09/Avg_avg_npc_048.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_026","id":87},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Scout","text":"瑞卡参军仅是为了报答殿下的恩情。","id":88,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/06/Avg_avg_npc_026.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Scout","text":"她曾对我说，为殿下而战是她唯一的愿望，是她生命的全部......","id":89,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/06/Avg_avg_npc_026.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_048","id":90},{"type":"dialogue","name":"博士","text":"请说下去，Scout，我在听。","id":91,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/09/Avg_avg_npc_048.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_026","id":92},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Scout","text":"......在卡兹戴尔，孩子们难有什么愿望，也难有想守护的事物。","id":93,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/06/Avg_avg_npc_026.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Scout","text":"他们只是被卷入战争，而后战死。","id":94,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/06/Avg_avg_npc_026.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_048","id":95},{"type":"dialogue","name":"博士","text":"所以你希望保留瑞卡的名誉，延续她守护殿下的愿望。","id":96,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/09/Avg_avg_npc_048.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":97},{"type":"character","id":98},{"type":"text","text":"Scout没有回答，身经百战的老兵又回归了沉默。","id":99},{"type":"text","text":"博士缓缓起身，伸手拍了拍Scout的肩膀。这是凯尔希没有预料到的。","id":100},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_048","id":101},{"type":"dialogue","name":"博士","text":"若刚才有任何冒犯，请原谅，我知道你一定会有很好的理由。","id":102,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/09/Avg_avg_npc_048.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"博士","text":"我的决定是，没有人会受到处分。但这样的处理结果是对军纪的损害，必定会招致非议。","id":103,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/09/Avg_avg_npc_048.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"博士","text":"Scout，我希望你和你的小队在未来用行动回应质疑。","id":104,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/09/Avg_avg_npc_048.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_026","id":105},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Scout","text":"一定。指挥官，女士，我先回去了。","id":106,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/06/Avg_avg_npc_026.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_048","id":107},{"type":"dialogue","name":"博士","text":"走之前答应我一件事。请至少把自己的生命和名誉，放在与其他队员同等的高度上。","id":108,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/09/Avg_avg_npc_048.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_026","id":109},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Scout","text":"我会的。","id":110,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/06/Avg_avg_npc_026.png"},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":111},{"type":"dialog","id":112},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":113},{"type":"character","id":114},{"type":"cameraeffect","effect":"Grayscale","keep":"true","amount":"0","fadetime":"0","id":115},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/8/8a/Avg_bg_bg_black.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":116},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":117},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":118},{"type":"image","y":"-150","fadetime":"0","xScale":"1.4","yScale":"1.4","id":119},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"3","block":"false","id":120},{"type":"imagetween","xScale":"1.4","yScale":"1.4","yFrom":"-150","yTo":"-100","duration":"20","ease":"OutQuad","block":"false","id":121},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":122},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"......此外，可露希尔或许会找你商讨伦蒂尼姆的问题，她很关心我在这件事上的立场。","id":123},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"你可以和她多分享一些决策过程，毕竟她也是潜在的作战成员。","id":124},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"当然，你们也可以......聊些别的。","id":125},{"type":"dialog","id":126},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":127},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":128},{"type":"image","id":129},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/c/c0/Avg_bg_bg_lungmencommand.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":130},{"type":"cameraeffect","effect":"Grayscale","keep":"true","amount":"0.7","fadetime":"0","id":131},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":132},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":133},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$m_dia_street_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/beta3_181101/m_dia_street_loop.mp3","volume":"0.4","id":134,"musicid":1},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":135},{"type":"text","text":"11:27 A.M. 天气/晴","id":136},{"type":"text","text":"罗德岛总工程师办公室","id":137},{"type":"dialog","id":138},{"type":"character","name":"char_003_kalts_1#2","name2":"char_007_closre_1","fadetime":"0.5","id":139},{"type":"delay","time":"0.51","id":140},{"type":"character","name":"char_003_kalts_1#2","name2":"char_007_closre_1","focus":"1","id":141},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"这次又是什么事。","id":142,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/f/fc/Avg_char_003_kalts_2.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_003_kalts_1#2","name2":"char_007_closre_1","focus":"2","id":143},{"type":"dialogue","name":"可露希尔","text":"凯尔希，去伦蒂尼姆的事有定论了吗？","id":144,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/0c/Avg_char_007_closre_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","name2":"char_007_closre_1","focus":"1","id":145},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"仍在讨论，行动本身确实存在风险。为什么突然关心这个。","id":146,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/d3/Avg_char_003_kalts_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","name2":"char_007_closre_1","focus":"2","id":147},{"type":"dialogue","name":"可露希尔","text":"担心你心情不好呗。我清楚你心底一定想去，却要考虑罗德岛面临的危险。","id":148,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/0c/Avg_char_007_closre_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"可露希尔","text":"纠结的时候可是最消耗精力的。","id":149,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/0c/Avg_char_007_closre_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","name2":"char_007_closre_1","focus":"1","id":150},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"不存在纠结，罗德岛的安全永远在首位。","id":151,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/d3/Avg_char_003_kalts_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","name2":"char_007_closre_1","focus":"2","id":152},{"type":"dialogue","name":"可露希尔","text":"如果哪天你能随心做想做的事该多好。","id":153,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/0c/Avg_char_007_closre_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"可露希尔","text":"这事可瞒不过我，凭你与特蕾西娅的友谊，伦蒂尼姆的事你无法置身事外。","id":154,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/0c/Avg_char_007_closre_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","name2":"char_007_closre_1","focus":"1","id":155},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"与殿下无关。我只关心行动本身对罗德岛的利弊。","id":156,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/d3/Avg_char_003_kalts_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","name2":"char_007_closre_1#6","focus":"2","id":157},{"type":"dialogue","name":"可露希尔","text":"你就是这样，总把责任挂在嘴边，至少偶尔也该关心一下自己。","id":158,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/47/Avg_char_007_closre_6.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","name2":"char_007_closre_1#4","focus":"2","id":159},{"type":"dialogue","name":"可露希尔","text":"麻烦的事丢给博士，咱俩去喝一杯倒倒苦水，多好。","id":160,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/8/81/Avg_char_007_closre_4.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","name2":"char_007_closre_1#4","focus":"1","id":161},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"博士已经很辛苦了。","id":162,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/d3/Avg_char_003_kalts_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","name2":"char_007_closre_1","focus":"2","id":163},{"type":"dialogue","name":"可露希尔","text":"那倒也是，虽然博士失忆前后转变挺大，但工作狂这点可完全没变。","id":164,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/0c/Avg_char_007_closre_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","name2":"char_007_closre_1#2","focus":"2","id":165},{"type":"dialogue","name":"可露希尔","text":"说起来，以前的博士可严肃了，还是现在这样比较好。","id":166,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/47/Avg_char_007_closre_2.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","name2":"char_007_closre_1#2","focus":"1","id":167},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"现在这样比较好欺负？","id":168,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/d3/Avg_char_003_kalts_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"我听说了，你上次给博士试用的跑步机会无端浮空，必须观看商品促销广告才能降落。","id":169,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/d3/Avg_char_003_kalts_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","name2":"char_007_closre_1#2","focus":"2","id":170},{"type":"dialogue","name":"可露希尔","text":"那可是限时大促，是在帮博士省钱。","id":171,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/47/Avg_char_007_closre_2.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_003_kalts_1#2","name2":"char_007_closre_1#2","focus":"1","id":172},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"我需要你多为博士着想一些。没人想在忙得焦头烂额时再受一些惊吓。","id":173,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/f/fc/Avg_char_003_kalts_2.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_003_kalts_1#2","name2":"char_007_closre_1#6","focus":"2","id":174},{"type":"dialogue","name":"可露希尔","text":"好好好，怎么突然这么严肃。","id":175,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/47/Avg_char_007_closre_6.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"可露希尔","text":"可能是有点怵失忆前的博士吧，我现在总想搞点恶作剧。","id":176,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/47/Avg_char_007_closre_6.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"可露希尔","text":"尤其是最后那段日子里，博士的表现越来越古怪......","id":177,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/47/Avg_char_007_closre_6.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_003_kalts_1#2","name2":"char_007_closre_1#6","focus":"1","id":178},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"打住，可露希尔，相关话题到此为止。更禁止你对博士提起这些。","id":179,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/f/fc/Avg_char_003_kalts_2.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_003_kalts_1#2","name2":"char_007_closre_1","focus":"2","id":180},{"type":"dialogue","name":"可露希尔","text":"放心吧，我有分寸。对了凯尔希，去伦蒂尼姆前，我准备开展对“待规划区”的整修，至少得对舰体材料进行加厚。","id":181,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/0c/Avg_char_007_closre_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"可露希尔","text":"虽说是一笔很大的开销，但作为可靠的工程师，我认为这点程度的投资还是非常有必要的。","id":182,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/0c/Avg_char_007_closre_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_003_kalts_1#2","name2":"char_007_closre_1#2","focus":"2","id":183},{"type":"dialogue","name":"可露希尔","text":"所以啊，我已经代表工程部决定了，奋战三天三夜，让“待规划区”焕然一新！","id":184,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/47/Avg_char_007_closre_2.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","name2":"char_007_closre_1#2","focus":"1","id":185},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"没有必要，“待规划区”是全舰最坚固的地方。","id":186,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/d3/Avg_char_003_kalts_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","name2":"char_007_closre_1#2","focus":"2","id":187},{"type":"dialogue","name":"可露希尔","text":"咳咳，这我可就有发言权了。“待规划区”的正下方是无人机机库，而机库没有任何支柱的支撑。","id":188,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/47/Avg_char_007_closre_2.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"可露希尔","text":"一旦上方遭到破坏，机库顶部就会变形，然后......","id":189,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/47/Avg_char_007_closre_2.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","name2":"char_007_closre_1#6","focus":"2","id":190},{"type":"dialogue","name":"可露希尔","text":"凯尔希，你干嘛这样盯着我，我害怕。","id":191,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/47/Avg_char_007_closre_6.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","name2":"char_007_closre_1#6","focus":"1","id":192},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"你只是自己想去罢了。","id":193,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/d3/Avg_char_003_kalts_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","name2":"char_007_closre_1","focus":"2","id":194},{"type":"dialogue","name":"可露希尔","text":"好吧，我摊牌了，作为总工程师有片区域进不去我好奇。","id":195,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/0c/Avg_char_007_closre_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","name2":"char_007_closre_1","focus":"1","id":196},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"我有我的考虑。","id":197,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/d3/Avg_char_003_kalts_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","name2":"char_007_closre_1","focus":"2","id":198},{"type":"dialogue","name":"可露希尔","text":"总把秘密藏着可是会憋坏的。","id":199,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/0c/Avg_char_007_closre_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"可露希尔","text":"凯尔希，什么时候能把你知道的和我分享一些，不要都自己扛着。","id":200,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/0c/Avg_char_007_closre_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","name2":"char_007_closre_1","focus":"1","id":201},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"或许......会有那么一天吧。","id":202,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/d3/Avg_char_003_kalts_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","name2":"char_007_closre_1","focus":"2","id":203},{"type":"dialogue","name":"可露希尔","text":"行吧。","id":204,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/0c/Avg_char_007_closre_1.png"},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":205},{"type":"dialog","id":206},{"type":"character","name":"char_empty","name2":"char_007_closre_1","fadetime":"1.5","id":207},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","volume":"1","id":208},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":209},{"type":"character","name":"char_empty","name2":"char_007_closre_1#6","id":210},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.3","xstrength":"30","ystrength":"30","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":211},{"type":"dialogue","name":"可露希尔","text":"嗯？你刚刚是不是松口了！？","id":212,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/b/bf/Avg_char_empty.png"},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"3","id":213},{"type":"dialog","id":214},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":215},{"type":"character","id":216},{"type":"cameraeffect","effect":"Grayscale","keep":"true","amount":"0","fadetime":"0","id":217},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/8/8a/Avg_bg_bg_black.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":218},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":219},{"type":"image","y":"0","fadetime":"0","xScale":"1.3","yScale":"1.3","id":220},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"3","block":"false","id":221},{"type":"imagetween","xScale":"1.3","yScale":"1.3","yFrom":"0","yTo":"30","duration":"20","ease":"OutQuad","block":"false","id":222},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":223},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"康纳郡的病患安置工作，今天会全部完成。近期需要你重新评估安置点的防卫力量。","id":224},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"医疗部晚些时候会把相关数据转交给你。","id":225},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"以后类似事务将逐步转交精英干员负责，不分散你在更重要的议题上的精力。","id":226},{"type":"dialog","id":227},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":228},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":229},{"type":"image","id":230},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/0d/Avg_bg_bg_infirmary.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":231},{"type":"cameraeffect","effect":"Grayscale","keep":"true","amount":"0.7","fadetime":"0","id":232},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":233},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":234},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$warm_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/act9d0d0/m_avg_warm_loop.mp3","volume":"0.4","id":235,"musicid":2},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":236},{"type":"character","name":"char_016_medic","fadetime":"0.5","id":237},{"type":"delay","time":"0.51","id":238},{"type":"character","name":"char_016_medic","id":239},{"type":"dialogue","name":"医疗干员","text":"抱歉打扰到各位了，大家都醒一醒。凯尔希医生即将开始每日的例行巡房。","id":240,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/39/Avg_char_016_medic.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_006","id":241},{"type":"dialogue","name":"普通感染者A","text":"今天的晚间巡房提早了不少呀......欸？还来了好多后勤部的干员。","id":242,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/e/e8/Avg_avg_npc_006.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_005","name2":"avg_npc_006","focus":"1","id":243},{"type":"dialogue","name":"普通感染者B","text":"你这老忘事的毛病啥时候也该让凯尔希医生给治治咯。","id":244,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/d5/Avg_avg_npc_005.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"普通感染者B","text":"医护小姑娘连续一周来咱病房打招呼，说准备把大家转移到康纳郡的临时医疗安置点。你这不是让人家口舌全白费嘛。","id":245,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/d5/Avg_avg_npc_005.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_016_medic","id":246},{"type":"dialogue","name":"医疗干员","text":"哈哈，不要紧的大伯，毕竟也是比较突然的安排。","id":247,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/39/Avg_char_016_medic.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"医疗干员","text":"这边再唠叨一下，罗德岛本舰近期会在维多利亚周边开展一系列模拟演习。","id":248,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/39/Avg_char_016_medic.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"医疗干员","text":"考虑到大家的安全，决定将各位暂时转移到康纳郡的医疗安置点。","id":249,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/39/Avg_char_016_medic.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"医疗干员","text":"请大家放心，康纳郡的医护设施齐全，且大部分医护人员也会陪同前往。","id":250,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/39/Avg_char_016_medic.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_006","name2":"char_003_kalts_1","focus":"1","id":251},{"type":"dialogue","name":"普通感染者A","text":"你看看，这才是艾莉——","id":252,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/e/e8/Avg_avg_npc_006.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_006","name2":"char_003_kalts_1","focus":"1","id":253},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.5","xstrength":"15","ystrength":"15","vibrato":"20","randomness":"70","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":254},{"type":"dialogue","name":"普通感染者A","text":"啊啊凯尔希医生！您什么时候站我边上的？瞧我这眼神......","id":255,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/e/e8/Avg_avg_npc_006.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":256},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_006","name2":"char_003_kalts_1","focus":"2","id":257},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"不要紧，我也刚到。","id":258,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/d3/Avg_char_003_kalts_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","id":259},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"艾莉，把这位病人今天的血液检测报告递给我。","id":260,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/d3/Avg_char_003_kalts_1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":261},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":262},{"type":"character","id":263},{"type":"delay","time":"0.1","id":264},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":265},{"type":"character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","id":266},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"嗯，你恢复得很快，矿石病也没有任何加重的迹象。","id":267,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/d3/Avg_char_003_kalts_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_006","name2":"char_003_kalts_1","focus":"1","id":268},{"type":"dialogue","name":"普通感染者A","text":"我能有今天全是托您的福。想当初矿石病急性发作的时候，您可是一天一夜没合眼地抢救，我这才......","id":269,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/e/e8/Avg_avg_npc_006.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_006","name2":"char_003_kalts_1","focus":"2","id":270},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"这只是我作为医生的职责。","id":271,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/d3/Avg_char_003_kalts_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"接下来要宣读转移安置的相关协议，宣读后需要你在协议上签字。根据《罗德岛矿石病收治规定》第四条......","id":272,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/d3/Avg_char_003_kalts_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_006","name2":"char_003_kalts_1","focus":"1","id":273},{"type":"dialogue","name":"普通感染者A","text":"医生您歇歇，不用念啦，我完完全全地信任罗德岛，直接让我签字就行。","id":274,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/e/e8/Avg_avg_npc_006.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_006","name2":"char_003_kalts_1","focus":"2","id":275},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"谢谢好意。但完整宣读协议也是为了保障你的权益。","id":276,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/d3/Avg_char_003_kalts_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","id":277},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"艾莉，时间有限，搬运病患的人手可能不太够，去走廊上看看有没有人能帮忙。","id":278,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/d3/Avg_char_003_kalts_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_016_medic","id":279},{"type":"dialogue","name":"医疗干员","text":"好的。","id":280,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/39/Avg_char_016_medic.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":281},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":282},{"type":"dialogue","name":"医疗干员","text":"啊，博士？下午好呀，您怎么在这里？","id":283,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/39/Avg_char_016_medic.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":284},{"type":"decision","options":{"1":{"id":"286","text":"下午好。"},"2":{"id":"286","text":"......"},"3":{"id":"286","text":"好久不见。"}},"values":[],"id":285},{"type":"predicate","references":["1","2","3"],"id":286,"end":288},{"type":"character","name":"char_016_medic","id":287},{"type":"dialogue","name":"医疗干员","text":"博士，你现在有空吗？我们这边转移安置病患的人手不太够，可能需要你的帮忙......","id":288,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/39/Avg_char_016_medic.png","end":true},{"type":"dialog","id":289},{"type":"decision","options":{"1":{"id":"291","text":"有空。"},"2":{"id":"291","text":"......行。"},"3":{"id":"291","text":"我非常愿意帮忙。"}},"values":[],"id":290},{"type":"predicate","references":["1","2","3"],"id":291,"end":293},{"type":"character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","id":292},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"......以你现在的身体情况，我并不建议你从事体力劳作。","id":293,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/d3/Avg_char_003_kalts_1.png","end":true},{"type":"dialog","id":294},{"type":"decision","options":{"1":{"id":"296","text":"闲着也是闲着。"},"2":{"id":"296","text":"......我会努力。"},"3":{"id":"296","text":"总得让我试试吧！别小看我！"}},"values":[],"id":295},{"type":"predicate","references":["1","2","3"],"id":296,"end":300},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_005","id":297},{"type":"dialogue","name":"普通感染者B","text":"博士......这不会是罗德岛指挥官吧？就是小艾莉天天挂在嘴边赞不绝口的那位？","id":298,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/d5/Avg_avg_npc_005.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_016_medic","id":299},{"type":"dialogue","name":"医疗干员","text":"大......大叔您可别乱说！博士，我之前只是在向他们介绍罗德岛呢。","id":300,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/39/Avg_char_016_medic.png","end":true},{"type":"dialog","id":301},{"type":"decision","options":{"1":{"id":"303","text":"我没她说的那么厉害。"},"2":{"id":"303","text":"......"},"3":{"id":"303","text":"我有这么帅气吗？"}},"values":[],"id":302},{"type":"predicate","references":["1","2","3"],"id":303,"end":307},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_006","id":304},{"type":"dialogue","name":"普通感染者A","text":"让罗德岛指挥官给我做转移安置？这使不得......","id":305,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/e/e8/Avg_avg_npc_006.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","id":306},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"不必推辞，哪怕是最细微的工作，罗德岛所有人也都有义务参与。战地指挥官的头衔并不会改变什么。","id":307,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/d3/Avg_char_003_kalts_1.png","end":true},{"type":"dialog","id":308},{"type":"character","id":309},{"type":"decision","options":{"1":{"id":"311","text":"时间有限，正式开始转移。"},"2":{"id":"311","text":"节省时间。"},"3":{"id":"311","text":"开始干活吧。"}},"values":[],"id":310},{"type":"predicate","references":["1","2","3"],"id":311},{"type":"decision","options":{"1":{"id":"313","text":"库斯，你过来抬大伯的上半身，注意医疗设备连接线。"}},"values":[],"id":312},{"type":"predicate","references":["1"],"id":313,"end":315},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_012","id":314},{"type":"dialogue","name":"后勤干员","text":"好嘞。艾莉，这台新的仪器是？之前从来没有见过。","id":315,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/1/1b/Avg_avg_npc_012.png","end":true},{"type":"dialog","id":316},{"type":"decision","options":{"1":{"id":"318","text":"融晶仪，莱茵生命CR-01实验型，内置源石回路。"}},"values":[],"id":317},{"type":"predicate","references":["1"],"id":318},{"type":"decision","options":{"1":{"id":"320","text":"中晚期矿石病患者体内被结晶填充，脏器易受损破裂。"}},"values":[],"id":319},{"type":"predicate","references":["1"],"id":320},{"type":"decision","options":{"1":{"id":"322","text":"融晶仪通过能量的有序集中释放对结晶进行消解。"}},"values":[],"id":321},{"type":"predicate","references":["1"],"id":322,"end":325},{"type":"character","name":"char_016_medic","id":323},{"type":"dialogue","name":"医疗干员","text":"是这样的没错！我就说吧，博士果然什么都知道。","id":324,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/39/Avg_char_016_medic.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_012","id":325,"end":true},{"type":"dialog","id":326},{"type":"decision","options":{"1":{"id":"328","text":"库斯，别那样直接抬。"},"2":{"id":"328","text":"库斯，住手。"},"3":{"id":"328","text":"库斯，停下！"}},"values":[],"id":327},{"type":"predicate","references":["1","2","3"],"id":328},{"type":"decision","options":{"1":{"id":"330","text":"左手把患者的双手并拢放在自己颈侧，右手抱紧双腿......"}},"values":[],"id":329},{"type":"predicate","references":["1"],"id":330,"end":335},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_012","id":331},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.3","xstrength":"30","ystrength":"30","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":332},{"type":"dialogue","name":"后勤干员","text":"对......对不起！之前凯尔希医生主讲的战地搬运课程我听得不太认真，很多知识点都没有记住......","id":333,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/1/1b/Avg_avg_npc_012.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","id":334},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"这种课程本就要靠实践去加深记忆。可博士你又是如何知道的？我记得开课期间你都在萨尔贡出外勤。","id":335,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/d3/Avg_char_003_kalts_1.png","end":true},{"type":"dialog","id":336},{"type":"decision","options":{"1":{"id":"338","text":"下意识就说出口了。"},"2":{"id":"338","text":"......"},"3":{"id":"338","text":"可能我是天才吧。"}},"values":[],"id":337},{"type":"predicate","references":["1","2","3"],"id":338,"end":339},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":339,"end":true},{"type":"dialog","id":340},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":341},{"type":"character","id":342},{"type":"cameraeffect","effect":"Grayscale","keep":"true","amount":"0","fadetime":"0","id":343},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/8/8a/Avg_bg_bg_black.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":344},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":345},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":346},{"type":"image","y":"-50","fadetime":"0","xScale":"1.2","yScale":"1.2","id":347},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"3","block":"false","id":348},{"type":"imagetween","xScale":"1.2","yScale":"1.2","yFrom":"-50","yTo":"-25","duration":"20","ease":"OutQuad","block":"false","id":349},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":350},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"最后一件事，阿米娅近期忙于伦蒂尼姆之行的各项评估，也请你抽出时间关心一下她。","id":351},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"她是罗德岛的领袖，但她同时也是个孩子。","id":352},{"type":"dialog","id":353},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":354},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":355},{"type":"image","id":356},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/5/53/Avg_bg_bg_rhodescom.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":357},{"type":"cameraeffect","effect":"Grayscale","keep":"true","amount":"0.7","fadetime":"0","id":358},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":359},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":360},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$newhope01_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/beta3_181101/m_dia_newhope01_loop.mp3","volume":"0.4","id":361,"musicid":3},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":362},{"type":"text","text":"2:29 A.M. 天气/阴","id":363},{"type":"text","text":"巴别塔临时作战指挥室","id":364},{"type":"dialog","id":365},{"type":"character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","id":366},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"你是巴别塔的领袖，但同时也是矿石病患者。请重视自己的身体。","id":367,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/d3/Avg_char_003_kalts_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"我建议你停止工作，立刻去休息。","id":368,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/d3/Avg_char_003_kalts_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_056","id":369},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"凯尔希，你还是这么会关心人......啊，博士，请进来吧，我们没有在讨论机密事项。","id":370,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/8/8f/Avg_avg_npc_056.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":371},{"type":"character","id":372},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","id":373},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_048","fadetime":"1.5","id":374},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":375},{"type":"dialogue","name":"博士","text":"我都听到了。殿下，你是该保证足够的睡眠时间。","id":376,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/09/Avg_avg_npc_048.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"博士","text":"昨晚的作战会议气氛很微妙，想必消耗了你大量的精力。","id":377,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/09/Avg_avg_npc_048.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_056","id":378},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"不必担心。倒是博士，我要为一些与会者的言辞道歉，他们无意冒犯，只是情绪稍有激动。","id":379,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/8/8f/Avg_avg_npc_056.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"他们担心我的安全，但我心里明白，博士一定考虑了所有可能的情况。这是最优解。","id":380,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/8/8f/Avg_avg_npc_056.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_048","id":381},{"type":"dialogue","name":"博士","text":"特雷西斯想夺回战争的主动权。他深知你的优势同时也是你的软肋。","id":382,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/09/Avg_avg_npc_048.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"博士","text":"但他想不到的是，你会为萨卡兹人作出多大的牺牲。","id":383,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/09/Avg_avg_npc_048.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"博士","text":"当阿斯卡纶率领的部队出现在小镇上时，他将会意识到自己败局已定。","id":384,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/09/Avg_avg_npc_048.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_056","id":385},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"你总是这么令人安心。博士，听你说话可比睡一觉让人精神多了。","id":386,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/8/8f/Avg_avg_npc_056.png"},{"type":"text","text":"特蕾西娅疲惫的脸上展露出一丝欣慰的笑，这份笑容在她看向门外时变得更加温柔了。","id":387},{"type":"dialog","id":388},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_056","id":389},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"快进来。来这边，坐我边上。","id":390,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/8/8f/Avg_avg_npc_056.png"},{"type":"character","id":391},{"type":"dialogue","name":"娇小的卡特斯","text":"可......可是......","id":392},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_056","id":393},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"别探头张望了，这里没有外人，阿米娅。","id":394,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/8/8f/Avg_avg_npc_056.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":395},{"type":"character","id":396},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","id":397},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_051","fadetime":"1.5","id":398},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":399},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"博士，凯尔希医生，晚......晚上好。","id":400,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/df/Avg_avg_npc_051.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"我不是故意这么晚还没休息的。","id":401,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/df/Avg_avg_npc_051.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_056","id":402},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"没人会责怪你。让我猜猜，做噩梦了？","id":403,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/8/8f/Avg_avg_npc_056.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_051","id":404},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"不......不是的。我是听到军队的集合声醒过来的。","id":405,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/df/Avg_avg_npc_051.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"我趴在窗户上看，阿斯卡纶姐姐似乎带着其他战士在为远行做准备......","id":406,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/df/Avg_avg_npc_051.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_048","id":407},{"type":"dialogue","name":"博士","text":"他们是有任务在身。","id":408,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/09/Avg_avg_npc_048.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_051","id":409},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"可是......可是阿斯卡纶姐姐说过，她绝对不会离开殿下和我哪怕一步。","id":410,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/df/Avg_avg_npc_051.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"我担心发生了什么事，就想着偷偷来指挥室看一眼......","id":411,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/df/Avg_avg_npc_051.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_056","id":412},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"阿米娅呀阿米娅，是博士交给了阿斯卡纶一个小任务，他们不用多久就会回来的。","id":413,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/8/8f/Avg_avg_npc_056.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"你想想，博士指挥的战斗，哪一次不是速战速决？","id":414,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/8/8f/Avg_avg_npc_056.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_051","id":415},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"确......确实，如果是博士的意见，我就放心了。","id":416,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/df/Avg_avg_npc_051.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"博士是最能给人安全感的。","id":417,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/df/Avg_avg_npc_051.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_048","id":418},{"type":"dialogue","name":"博士","text":"阿米娅，你该休息了。","id":419,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/09/Avg_avg_npc_048.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_051","id":420},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"我这就回去！大家晚安。","id":421,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/df/Avg_avg_npc_051.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":422},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","id":423},{"type":"character","fadetime":"1.5","id":424},{"type":"delay","time":"1.5","id":425},{"type":"dialog","id":426},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_056","id":427},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"真是令人怜爱的孩子......","id":428,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/8/8f/Avg_avg_npc_056.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"博士，你来之前我确实在担心......阿斯卡纶离开期间罗德岛舰船的安全问题。","id":429,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/8/8f/Avg_avg_npc_056.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_048","id":430},{"type":"dialogue","name":"博士","text":"担心是正常的。","id":431,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/09/Avg_avg_npc_048.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"博士","text":"拉长战线的同时，包围一个毫无战略意义的小镇。特雷西斯的真正目的无从得知。","id":432,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/09/Avg_avg_npc_048.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_056","id":433},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"我的安危倒是其次，更多的是担心连累到舰上的研究人员和孩子们。","id":434,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/8/8f/Avg_avg_npc_056.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"但正如阿米娅所说，你确实能给人带来安全感。在你指挥下所取得的战果也令人无从置疑。","id":435,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/8/8f/Avg_avg_npc_056.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"博士，凯尔希，战争胜利的那天，应该不远了吧？","id":436,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/8/8f/Avg_avg_npc_056.png"},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":437},{"type":"dialog","id":438},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":439},{"type":"character","id":440},{"type":"cameraeffect","effect":"Grayscale","keep":"true","amount":"0","fadetime":"0","id":441},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/8/8a/Avg_bg_bg_black.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":442},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":443},{"type":"image","y":"-20","fadetime":"0","xScale":"1.1","yScale":"1.1","id":444},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"3","block":"false","id":445},{"type":"imagetween","xScale":"1.1","yScale":"1.1","yFrom":"-20","yTo":"20","duration":"30","ease":"OutQuad","block":"false","id":446},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":447},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"刚才说的事，都是在你常规日程之外的......","id":448},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"博士，你还在听吗？","id":449},{"type":"dialog","id":450},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":451},{"type":"decision","options":{"1":{"id":"453","text":"我在听。"},"2":{"id":"453","text":"......"},"3":{"id":"453","text":"听着呢，很清楚。"}},"values":[],"id":452},{"type":"predicate","references":["1","2","3"],"id":453,"end":462},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":454},{"type":"image","id":455},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$loneliness_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/static/m_avg/m_avg_loneliness_loop.mp3","volume":"0.4","id":456,"musicid":4},{"type":"image","xScale":"1.1","yScaleFrom":"1.1","x":"50","fadetime":"0","id":457},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"3","block":"false","id":458},{"type":"imagetween","xScale":"1.1","yScaleFrom":"1.1","xFrom":"50","xTo":"-50","duration":"50","ease":"Linear","block":"false","id":459},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":460},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":461},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"博士，怎样才算真正地活着？","id":462,"end":true},{"type":"dialog","id":463},{"type":"decision","options":{"1":{"id":"465","text":"这问题有些突然。"},"2":{"id":"465","text":"......没想过。"},"3":{"id":"465","text":"这问题也太深刻了。"}},"values":[],"id":464},{"type":"predicate","references":["1","2","3"],"id":465,"end":466},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"服从他人意志，失去前行的理由，这算活着吗？","id":466,"end":true},{"type":"dialog","id":467},{"type":"decision","options":{"1":{"id":"469","text":"那不过是行尸走肉。"},"2":{"id":"469","text":"......"},"3":{"id":"469","text":"那是机器人吧？"}},"values":[],"id":468},{"type":"predicate","references":["1","2","3"],"id":469,"end":470},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"保有躯体，抽离记忆，又算活着吗？","id":470,"end":true},{"type":"dialog","id":471},{"type":"decision","options":{"1":{"id":"473","text":"那或许会活得有些茫然。"},"2":{"id":"473","text":"......"},"3":{"id":"473","text":"这说的是我吧？"}},"values":[],"id":472},{"type":"predicate","references":["1","2","3"],"id":473,"end":474},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"若二者择其一，博士，你会如何抉择？","id":474,"end":true},{"type":"dialog","id":475},{"type":"decision","options":{"1":{"id":"477","text":"我选择成为人，而非傀儡。"},"2":{"id":"477","text":"我会选择自由。"},"3":{"id":"477","text":"谁会想做机器？"}},"values":[],"id":476},{"type":"predicate","references":["1","2","3"],"id":477,"end":486},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":478},{"type":"blocker","a":"0.6","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":479},{"type":"subtitle","text":"凯尔希将意味深长的目光投向了你。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":480},{"type":"subtitle","id":481},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":482},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":483},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"自由是有代价的。","id":484},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"失去记忆后醒来，被迫去战斗，被迫见证牺牲。一路走来我们并未给你太多选择......","id":485},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"......看着我的眼睛。告诉我，博士，你究竟为何而战？","id":486,"end":true},{"type":"dialog","id":487},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":488},{"type":"blocker","a":"0.6","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":489},{"type":"subtitle","text":"记忆在此刻不断涌现，自切尔诺伯格苏醒后所发生的一切历历在目，喜悦与悲伤交织在一起......","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":490},{"type":"subtitle","text":"一个答案在你脑海中越来越清晰。你几乎下意识地脱口而出——","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":491},{"type":"subtitle","id":492},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":493},{"type":"decision","options":{"1":{"id":"495","text":"我为反抗自己的命运而战。"},"2":{"id":"495","text":"我为罗德岛而战。"},"3":{"id":"495","text":"我为守护这片大地而战。"}},"values":[],"id":494},{"type":"predicate","references":["1","2","3"],"id":495,"end":499},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":496},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"那请你不要忘记此刻的回答。","id":497},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"即使没有人能理解，我们也必须要这样走下去。","id":498},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"博士，而你也会找到你的道路。","id":499,"end":true},{"type":"dialog","id":500},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":501},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":502},{"type":"image","id":503},{"type":"dialog","id":504},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"3","id":505},{"type":"character","id":506},{"type":"image","id":507}],"characters":["？？？","凯尔希","博士","Scout","可露希尔","医疗干员","普通感染者A","普通感染者B","后勤干员","特蕾西娅","娇小的卡特斯","阿米娅"]}